data.description: Wow! Completely remodeled one story brick beauty with 4 BDRMS, 2 BATHS and two living areas. This home features: REFRIGERATED AIR, xeriscaped front landscaping, fresh exterior paint, new double French entry doors. Recessed lighting and fresh interior paint throughout home, newly textured walls and ceilings, updated kitchen with new wood countertops, SS appliances, new cabinets, breakfast nook. Family room with brick fireplace that serves as the focal point. All secondary bedrooms with new closet doors. Updated guest bathroom with new cabinets, new vanity and amazing shower/ tub combo. Master bedroom with huge walk in closet, updated master bathroom with new vanity, updated walk in shower. New plumbing and lighting fixtures throughout, new door knobs, new door hinges, new windows. Two doors to access backyard. Walking distance to Andress HS plus much, much more!
